<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us | LiAlvaro Apparel</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --orange: #FF6B2B;
      --orange-deep: #E8521A;
      --bg: #FAFAFA;
      --surface: #FFFFFF;
      --border: #E5E5EA;
      --text-primary: #1D1D1F;
      --text-secondary: #6E6E73;
      --shadow-md: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --radius-lg: 24px;
      --radius-xl: 32px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text-primary); }
    .container { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; }

    .topbar { background: var(--text-primary); text-align: center; padding: 9px 0; }
    .topbar p { font-size: 12.5px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); }
    .topbar a { color: var(--orange); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }

    nav {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px); background: rgba(250,250,250,0.85);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #F0F0F5; height: 56px;
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; height: 100%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-logo img { height: 34px; display: block; width: auto; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 26px; }
    .nav-links a { color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none; font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 600; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }
    .nav-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .btn-phone {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-phone svg { width: 13px; height: 13px; }
    .btn-phone:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--orange); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 999px;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--orange-deep); }

    .hero {
      padding: 110px 0 70px; text-align: center; background: var(--surface);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hero p { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-secondary); }

    .section { padding: 88px 0; }
    .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .panel {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid #F0F0F5; border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      padding: 34px 30px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }
    .panel h2 { font-size: 34px; letter-spacing: -0.025em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .panel p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; }
    .stack { display: grid; gap: 16px; }
    .mini {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid #F0F0F5; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .mini h3 { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .mini p { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65; font-size: 14.5px; }
    .inline-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #22856C;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .inline-cta:hover { background: #1b6f5a; }

    .cta {
      text-align: center; padding: 70px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #F5F5F7 100%);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .cta h2 { font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 58px); letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta p { color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 24px; }
    .cta a {
      display: inline-flex; text-decoration: none; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      background: #22856C; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 999px; padding: 14px 28px;
    }
    .cta a:hover { background: #1b6f5a; }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .container, .nav-inner { padding: 0 22px; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav-links, .btn-phone { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <p>Same-day service available in Los Angeles · Call <a href="tel:3109042655">(310) 904-2655</a></p>
  </div>
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo" aria-label="LiAlvaro Home"><img src="/brand/logo.png" alt="LiAlvaro" /></a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/design-your-apparel">Design Your Apparel</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#faq">FAQ</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles">Articles</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="nav-actions">
        <a href="tel:3109042655" class="btn-phone">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3.7 1C3.3 1 2.5 1.3 1.9 2L1 3c-.7.7-1 2 .3 4 .7 1.2 1.7 2.6 3.1 4s2.8 2.4 4 3.1c2 1.3 3.3 1 4 .3l1-1c.7-.7 1-1.5 1-1.9 0-.2-.2-.5-.5-.7L12 9.5c-.3-.2-.6-.3-.8-.2l-1.3.4c-.3.1-.6 0-.8-.2L7.5 8l-1.5-1.6c-.2-.2-.3-.5-.2-.8L6.2 4.4c.1-.2 0-.5-.2-.8L4.4 1.5C4.2 1.2 3.9 1 3.7 1z"/></svg>
          (310) 904-2655
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="nav-cta">Get a Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>The story behind the print.</h1>
      <p>Born in Los Angeles, LiAlvaro Apparel was founded by artists who understand the power of a perfect garment and the impact a great print can make.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container grid">
      <article class="panel">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          Lialvaro Apparel is a rising star in the Los Angeles T-shirt printing and embroidery scene, bringing its fresh and vibrant designs to the city since 2020. Founded by a passionate team of artists and entrepreneurs, Lialvaro Apparel quickly gained recognition for its high-quality printing, unique designs, and commitment to ethical and sustainable practices. From eye-catching custom creations for individuals and businesses to trendy collections that capture the LA vibe, Lialvaro Apparel has something for everyone. Whether you're looking for a statement T-shirt to express your individuality or a stylish way to promote your brand, Lialvaro Apparel is sure to have the perfect design and printing technique to bring your vision to life.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
          In addition to their exceptional printing and embroidery services, Lialvaro Apparel is also dedicated to giving back to the community. They partner with local organizations to support social causes and promote sustainability, making them a brand you can feel good about wearing. So, if you're in Los Angeles and looking for a high-quality, stylish, and socially conscious T-shirt or embroidered garment, look no further than Lialvaro Apparel.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-cta">Start an order</a>
        </p>
      </article>
      <div class="stack">
        <article class="mini">
          <h3>Our vision</h3>
          <p>From bold streetwear to delicate embroidery, we'll bridge the gap between dream and fabric, celebrating the diverse narratives that dance beneath the LA sun. Forget faceless merch, ours will be a haven for the dreamers, the doers, the artists, the hustlers. We'll be the canvas, the needle, the ink; you, the masterpiece.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="mini">
          <h3>Our promise</h3>
          <p>We will continue helping you tell your story, sticth by stitch and with every droplet of ink. We promise to remain relevant enough for you to rely on us for your brands, special events, or anything else brilliant enough to be called yours.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-cta">Start an order</a>
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Start a new design project</h2>
      <p>Tell us what you need, and we will help you choose the right print method, garment, and turnaround.</p>
      <a href="/contact">Get a Free Quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
